summary: Shanoa tattoo for CBBE,use Calientes Texture Blender
descriptionHtml:
Hi,everyone.You kown NPR made [url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/52431]Shanoa armor[/url],but there is no tattoo.So I try to make one.Hope you like it.

Installation:
First,you need [url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/5737]Calientes Texture Blender[/url]
Second,extract my tattoo *.png to "..Skyrim/Data/CalienteTools/Calientes Texture Blender/Library/Body and Feet/Color/Tatoos" folder
third,use TexBlend.exe and blend images

Enjoy
author: Laions
